  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MADNESS is a crazy racing game where you smash cars and perform tricks in the air-  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the cult classic derby racing game Need For Madness?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock cars as you progress through each stage </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose whether to win by wrecking all other cars or by placing 1st</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's up to you !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge and weave between aggressive AI opponents in order to survive the race</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Getting hit will hurt and it will send you flying</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform wild stunts in the air to gain power and speed </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Succumb to the MADNESS</p>",
